Ability object has :
1) function taht gets triggered when it is picked.
    That function will activate one time action or  
    add the SECONF dunction to an object abilityArray
2) SECOND function is a function that gets triggered every time    
    in update/fire/draw function of the targeted object for
    period described in duration variable of that abilityArray
3) duartion variable that goes with SECOND function